Description: Performs recurrence quantification analysis (RQA) for time series. Provides fast CPU and GPU-accelerated implementations for computing recurrence plots and standard RQA measures, including recurrence rate (RR), determinism (DET), laminarity (LAM), trapping time (TT), and entropy of diagonal line lengths (ENTR).
